Call OUVRE_TRACE("") From LECFIC
Local File ADOSSIER [F:ADS]
Read [F:ADS]DOSSIER = "GX3APP"
If !fstat
    Call AMAJ
    Call MAJ
Endif
Call SUPP_TRACE From LECFIC
Call LEC_TRACE From LECFIC
End
